sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Annie (User)
    participant VAD as Voice Activity Detection
    participant AgentOut as Agent Output Task
    participant AgentIn as Agent Input Task

    Note over User, AgentIn: INTERRUPTION HANDLING — WHAT SEPARATES VOICE AI FROM A RECORDING

    AgentOut->>User: "I'd recommend the navy blazer because it—"
    
    Note over User: Annie Interrupts
    User->>VAD: "Actually wait, I changed my mind"
    
    par Two concurrent asyncio tasks — neither blocks the other
        VAD->>AgentOut: Detects voice activity
        Note over AgentOut: Agent stops mid-sentence
        AgentOut-->>User: (Audio playback halted)
    and
        VAD->>AgentIn: Streams new audio
        Note over AgentIn: Processes Annie's interruption immediately
        AgentIn-->>AgentOut: Generate new response
        AgentOut->>User: Responds to new direction
    end
